CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 26, 1956, pg. A18 reads: "For Achievement - Mrs. Robert L. Vann, right, presents Certificate of Merit to some of the outstanding women cited at the 25th annual "Women's Day" program at First Baptist Church in Penn Township. Left to right: Mmes. Carrie Bullock, Helen Monk Bette, Annette Robinson, Elaine Gibson and Bessie Hairston."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: Carrie Bullock, Helen Monk Bette, Annette Robinson, Elaine Gibson, Bessie Hairston, and Jessie Vann, gathered for twenty-fifth annual Women's Day program in First Baptist Church, Penn Township
